Cost or Pricing Data_ Modifications. * * * * * Subcontractor Cost or Pricing Data_Modifications (Nov 1994) (a) The requirements of paragraphs (b) and (c) of this clause shall (1) become operative only for any modification to this contract involving a pricing adjustment expected to exceed the threshold for submission of cost or pricing data at (FAR) 48 CFR 15.804&hyph;2(a)(1); and (2) be limited to such modifications. (b) Before awarding any subcontract expected to exceed the threshold for submission of cost or pricing data at (FAR) 48 CFR 15.804&hyph;2(a)(1) when entered into, or pricing any subcontract modification involving a pricing adjustment expected to exceed the threshold for submission of cost or pricing data at (FAR) 48 CFR 15.804&hyph;2(a)(1), the Contractor shall require the subcontractor to submit cost or pricing data (actually or by specific identification in writing), unless the price is_ * * * * * (d) The Contractor shall insert the substance of this clause, including this paragraph (d), in each subcontract that exceeds the threshold for submission of cost or pricing data at (FAR) 48 CFR 15.804&hyph;2(a)(1), when entered into. (End of clause) 52.215&hyph;32 [Removed and Reserved] 12. Section 52.215&hyph;32 is removed and reserved. 52.215&hyph;37 [Removed and Reserved] 13. Section 52.215&hyph;37 is removed and reserved. [FR Doc. 94&hyph;29811 Filed 12&hyph;2&hyph;94; 8:45 am] BILLING CODE 6820&hyph;34&hyph;U
